	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Evac shelter</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><div class="mw-revision"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 04:38, 14 April 2022 by <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/User:Valar55" class="mw-userlink" title="User:Valar55"><bdi>Valar55</bdi></a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=User_talk:Valar55&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-usertoollinks-talk" title="User talk:Valar55 (page does not exist)">talk</a> | <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Special:Contributions/Valar55" class="mw-usertoollinks-contribs" title="Special:Contributions/Valar55">contribs</a>)</span></div><div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Evac_shelter&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=40315" title="Evac shelter">diff</a>) <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Evac_shelter&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=40315" title="Evac shelter">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div></div>
		
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><br />
</p>
<table class="infobox" cellspacing="5" style="width: 22em; text-align: left; font-size: 88%; line-height: 1.5em; width: 150px;">
